plot: Jeana decides its time to bond with her daughter Kara -- by inviting her to an exclusive diamond-shopping trip, Kimberly and Jo prepare to play a tennis match with women from the very competitive and elite Women's Tennis League, and Jo and Slade have an emotional confrontation that brings more questions than answers about the relationship. Vicki is excited to join the diamond-shopping trip, where she contemplates a new setting for her wedding ring. Doing better financially, Lauri joins Vicki and Jeana on the diamond-shopping spree in Beverly Hills, and it's time to celebrate as the 'housewives' gather for Kimberly's 45th birthday.—Anonymous
